WEBVTT

00:01.702 --> 00:03.404
(man) PREVIOUSLY ON
ABC's "FLASHFORWARD"...

00:03.404 --> 00:05.136
(woman) ALL WE KNOW FOR CERTAIN
IS THAT EVERYONE ON THE PLANET

00:05.136 --> 00:07.738
SEEMED TO HAVE BLACKED OUT
AT EXACTLY THE SAME TIME.

00:07.738 --> 00:10.211
YOU SHUT OFF
THE CONSCIOUSNESS

00:10.211 --> 00:13.084
OF THE ENTIRE HUMAN RACE
FOR 2 MINUTES, 17 SECONDS.

00:13.084 --> 00:15.146
I DIDN'T JUST
LOSE CONSCIOUSNESS.

00:15.146 --> 00:16.787
IT FELT MORE LIKE
I WAS HAVING A MEMORY,

00:16.787 --> 00:18.619
ONLY IT WAS IN THE FUTURE.
THE SAME THING HAPPENED TO ME.

00:18.619 --> 00:20.691
SO YOU'RE SAYING
EVERYONE'S CONSCIOUSNESS

00:20.691 --> 00:24.024
JUST JUMPED FORWARD SIX MONTHS?
CRAZY AS THAT SOUNDS, YEAH.

00:24.024 --> 00:25.496
PRIORITY NUMBER ONE--
FINDING OUT WHAT CAUSED THIS.

00:25.496 --> 00:27.798
IN MY FLASH-FORWARD,
I SEEMED TO HAVE AN IDEA

00:27.798 --> 00:31.332
WHY ALL THIS WAS HAPPENING.
I WAS GETTING
A PRENATAL SONOGRAM.

00:31.332 --> 00:34.665
I'M OBVIOUSLY NOT PREGNANT.
I WAS WITH ANOTHER MAN.

00:34.665 --> 00:38.609
(voice breaking)
I'VE NEVER SEEN HIM BEFORE.
I DIDN'T SEE A DAMN THING.
WHAT IF I DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING

00:38.609 --> 00:41.542
BECAUSE SIX MONTHS FROM NOW,
I'M GONNA BE DEAD?
WHAT HAVE YOU GOT
ON YOUR HAND?

00:41.542 --> 00:44.175
SOMETHING I MADE FOR YOU.
WHAT DO YOU GOT?

00:44.175 --> 00:46.147
AN 8-YEAR-OLD BOY. CAR PLOWED
STRAIGHT THROUGH A FENCE

00:46.147 --> 00:48.479
AT AN ELEMENTARY SCHOOL.
YOU'RE GONNA BE OKAY, HONEY.

00:48.479 --> 00:51.051
I KNOW, OLIVIA.
HOW DID YOU KNOW MY NAME?

00:51.051 --> 00:53.053
RIGHT THERE.
LOOK RIGHT THERE.
NO WAY.

00:53.053 --> 00:55.686
WHO THE HELL IS THAT?
AND WHY ARE THEY AWAKE?
I'M SORRY. YOU ARE?

00:55.686 --> 00:59.090
HIS FATHER--LLOYD SIMCOE.

