(rip)

02:32.523 --> 02:35.186
(woman grunts) CHARLIE!

02:35.186 --> 02:38.429
CHARLIE! CHARLIE, YOU KNOW
WE DON'T HIT AT SCHOOL.

02:38.429 --> 02:41.161
(grunts)
YOU'RE COMING WITH ME RIGHT NOW,
YOUNG LADY--CH--CHARLIE!

02:41.161 --> 02:42.463
(woman) COME BACK HERE!
(grunting)

02:42.463 --> 02:44.665
CHARLIE! COME BACK HERE!

02:44.665 --> 02:46.937
