30:20.950 --> 30:24.823
â™ª POCKETFUL OF POSIES â™ª
(whispers) CRAP.

30:24.823 --> 30:28.357
â™ª ASHES, ASHES,
WE ALL FALL DOWN â™ª

30:28.357 --> 30:30.900
FBI! OPEN UP!

30:30.900 --> 30:32.932
â™ª WE ALL FALL DOWN â™ª
D. GIBBONS, GET DOWN!

30:32.932 --> 30:35.965
FREEZE! DON'T MOVE!
ON YOUR KNEES!

