ARE YOU ALONE HERE?!
ON YOUR KNEES! DON'T MOVE!

30:38.607 --> 30:40.970
DOWN! GET DOWN!
GET ON YOUR KNEES!

30:40.970 --> 30:43.142
(liquid bubbling)
GET DOWN!

30:43.142 --> 30:45.975
(man)
"HE WHO FORESEES CALAMITIES

30:45.975 --> 30:48.878
SUFFERS THEM TWICE OVER."
WHAT'D YOU SAY?

30:50.950 --> 30:52.882
(flames whoosh)

30:54.383 --> 30:55.454
(grunts)

30:55.454 --> 30:56.926
(gunfire)

30:56.926 --> 30:59.028
(bullet ricochets)
OFFICER DOWN!

31:02.992 --> 31:06.465
(loud explosion)

31:17.346 --> 31:20.279
(siren wailing in distance)

31:20.279 --> 31:22.982
ALL RIGHT, FELLAS,
TAKE HER AWAY.

31:22.982 --> 31:27.286
(woman speaking indistinctly
over police radio)

31:27.286 --> 31:29.989
(camera shutter clicking)

31:33.993 --> 31:36.996
EXCUSE ME. COULD I TAKE A LOOK
AT THE PHOTO YOU JUST TOOK?

31:43.502 --> 31:45.074
(whoosh)

31:49.478 --> 31:52.011
(woman) 3-8-75, repeat
the location and stand by.

31:52.011 --> 31:54.143
THANKS.

31:54.143 --> 31:55.614
SHOOTER'S IN THE WIND.

31:55.614 --> 31:58.147
HEY, DEM, I'M--
I'M SORRY ABOUT KEEGAN.

31:58.147 --> 32:00.149
I KNOW WHAT YOU MUST
BE THINKING BUT--

32:00.149 --> 32:03.052
CAN WE TALK
ABOUT THAT LATER?

32:04.954 --> 32:08.527
WHAT WE GOT NOW IS
CELL PHONE AND WHITE QUEEN.

32:08.527 --> 32:11.130
SO WHO'S OUR BOBBY FISCHER
PLAYING CHESS WITH?

32:11.130 --> 32:13.132
EXACTLY.
CHESS PIECES, DOLLS.

32:13.132 --> 32:15.034
WHAT THE HELL
WAS HE DOING HERE, DEM?

32:15.034 --> 32:17.006
E.R.T. GUY'S BEST GUESS
IS HE WAS DOING SOME

32:17.006 --> 32:20.069
HEAVY DUTY COMPUTER HACKING.
ACCORDING TO DATA FORENSICS,

32:20.069 --> 32:22.972
OUR GUY'S BEEN SUPERBUSY
SINCE THE BLACKOUT.

32:22.972 --> 32:25.414
HE'S BEEN HACKING INTO NETS
ALL OVER THE WORLD--

32:25.414 --> 32:28.147
V.L.A. NEW MEXICO,
PARTICLE COLLIDER AT C.E.R.N.,

32:28.147 --> 32:29.518
G.P.S. NETWORK.

32:29.518 --> 32:32.151
HE EVEN TRIED TO HACK
INTO MOSAIC THROUGH THE N.S.A.
WHY?

32:32.151 --> 32:34.483
I THINK HE WAS RULING OUT
POSSIBLE CAUSES.

32:36.625 --> 32:39.188
I DON'T THINK WE'RE
THE ONLY ONES INVESTIGATING

32:39.188 --> 32:41.190
WHY THE BLACKOUT HAPPENED.

32:48.137 --> 32:49.468
DR. BENFORD.

32:49.468 --> 32:52.541
YOUR PATIENT PULLED THROUGH,
I SEE.

32:52.541 --> 32:55.704
(chuckles) I'M SORRY I DIDN'T
GET TO SEE YOUR SON TODAY.

32:55.704 --> 32:59.008
I WAS REALLY BUSY.
ALL HUMAN PATIENTS, I SWEAR.

33:00.349 --> 33:02.281
I SHOULD GET HER HOME.

33:02.281 --> 33:04.683
AH, YOU KNOW,
I'VE BEEN SITTING HERE,

33:04.683 --> 33:08.257
THINKING OF A WAY TO TELL MY SON
THAT HIS MOTHER IS DEAD.

33:12.621 --> 33:15.064
WELL...

33:15.064 --> 33:16.695
HOWEVER YOU TELL HIM,

33:16.695 --> 33:18.697
JUST BE SURE
TO TELL HIM YOU LOVE HIM.

33:20.729 --> 33:23.032
IS PARENTING
REALLY THAT SIMPLE?

33:23.032 --> 33:26.075
IT'S THE ONLY SIMPLE PART.

33:28.307 --> 33:30.479
TAKE CARE, MR. SIMCOE.

33:30.479 --> 33:34.183
(Nick Drake's "Place to Be"
playing)

33:39.748 --> 33:41.050
(whoosh)

33:41.050 --> 33:43.052
â™ª WHEN I WAS YOUNG â™ª

33:43.052 --> 33:45.424
â™ª YOUNGER THAN BEFORE â™ª

33:48.457 --> 33:52.261
â™ª I NEVER SAW THE TRUTH
HANGING... â™ª

33:52.261 --> 33:54.303
(whoosh)

33:57.436 --> 34:00.539
â™ª AND NOW I'M OLDER â™ª

34:00.539 --> 34:02.371
â™ª SEE IT FACE-TO-FACE â™ª

34:02.371 --> 34:04.373
(exhales deeply)

34:06.145 --> 34:09.278
â™ª AND NOW I'M OLDER â™ª

34:09.278 --> 34:12.281
â™ª GOTTA GET UP,
CLEAN THE PLACE â™ª

34:12.281 --> 34:14.123
I'M BACK, DYLAN.

34:20.189 --> 34:22.691
NOW THERE'S SOMETHING
I'VE...

34:22.691 --> 34:25.094
BEEN PUTTING OFF
TELLING YOU,

34:25.094 --> 34:29.338
BECAUSE I WANTED YOU
TO GET BETTER FIRST.

34:29.338 --> 34:32.501
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

34:32.501 --> 34:34.803
OH, YOU REALLY ARE
GETTING BETTER.

34:37.146 --> 34:39.478
I GUESS YOU'RE...

34:39.478 --> 34:41.480
YEAH,
I GUESS YOU'RE WONDERING

34:41.480 --> 34:43.852
WHY YOUR MOTHER
HASN'T COME TO SEE YOU YET.

34:43.852 --> 34:45.614
SHE...

34:45.614 --> 34:47.786
SHE'S NOT HERE.

34:50.589 --> 34:51.860
(sighs)

34:51.860 --> 34:53.862
YEAH, THAT'S R--
T-THAT'S RIGHT.

34:53.862 --> 34:55.394
UM...

34:57.166 --> 35:01.270
YOU SEE, DYLAN, UM...

35:01.270 --> 35:05.534
WHEN THE BLACKOUT HAPPENED,

35:05.534 --> 35:07.876
AND WHEN EVERYONE
FELL ASLEEP...

35:10.339 --> 35:12.441
(whispers) YOUR...

35:12.441 --> 35:15.144
(normal voice) YOUR MOTHER
NEVER WOKE UP AGAIN.

35:17.846 --> 35:20.789
SHE WAS IN AN ACCIDENT,
AND SHE, UM...

35:20.789 --> 35:23.852
SHE DIED?

35:30.459 --> 35:31.630
YEAH.

35:35.133 --> 35:36.565
(sniffles)

35:38.807 --> 35:40.509
BUT...

35:40.509 --> 35:44.913
IT'S JUST YOU AND ME NOW,
KIDDO,

35:44.913 --> 35:47.276
BUT WE'RE GONNA BE OKAY.

35:53.622 --> 35:55.824
(whispers) I LOVE YOU.

35:55.824 --> 35:58.387
I WANNA SEE OLIVIA.

36:04.493 --> 36:06.164
3:00 A.M., GUYS.

36:06.164 --> 36:09.167
I WAS JUST ABOUT TO FALL ASLEEP.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

36:09.167 --> 36:11.240
WHAT'S GOING ON
IS THAT I'M EATING CROW.

36:11.240 --> 36:12.901
TELL HIM.

36:12.901 --> 36:15.374
I MANAGED TO PULL
THE I.M.E.I. NUMBER

36:15.374 --> 36:18.507
OFF THE CELL YOU AND MARK
RECOVERED FROM UTAH.

36:18.507 --> 36:22.581
AND AS IT TURNS OUT, D. GIBBONS
MADE A SERIES OF SIX CALLS--

36:22.581 --> 36:25.914
FIVE RIGHT BEFORE THE BLACKOUT
TO ANOTHER DISPOSABLE CELL.

36:25.914 --> 36:27.916
WELL, A LOT OF PEOPLE MADE CALLS
BEFORE THE BLACKOUT.

36:27.916 --> 36:31.189
MARK WAS ON THE PHONE WITH YOU
WHEN IT HAPPENED.
YEAH, I KNOW,

36:31.189 --> 36:33.862
BUT THE SIXTH CALL WAS PLACED
30 SECONDS INTO THE BLACKOUT.

36:33.862 --> 36:36.665
I TRACED IT...
(types)

36:36.665 --> 36:39.197
TO ANOTHER CELL.

36:39.197 --> 36:41.199
D. GIBBONS WAS
ON THE PHONE WITH SOMEBODY ELSE

36:41.199 --> 36:44.603
DURING THE BLACKOUT.
YES, BUT NOT JUST
ANY SOMEBODY.

36:44.603 --> 36:47.436
(types)
THE SECOND CALL WAS PLACED

36:47.436 --> 36:49.438
TO SOMEONE WITHIN RANGE
OF THREE CELL PHONE TOWERS,

36:49.438 --> 36:51.880
ALLOWING ME TO TRIANGULATE
A POSITION.

36:51.880 --> 36:53.882
LET ME ASK YOU THIS--

36:53.882 --> 36:56.214
WHAT KIND OF A PLACE
HAS MULTIPLE TOWERS

36:56.214 --> 36:58.917
TO HANDLE
INCREASED CELL TRAFFIC?
A BASEBALL STADIUM.

36:58.917 --> 36:59.918
YEP.

36:59.918 --> 37:02.851
D. GIBBONS WAS TALKING...
(types)

37:02.851 --> 37:04.993
TO SUSPECT ZERO.

37:04.993 --> 37:08.527
AND THEN THERE WERE... TWO.

37:20.369 --> 37:22.271
HOW MANY POSTINGS SO FAR?

37:22.271 --> 37:24.513
(types)
900,000 AND COUNTING.

37:24.513 --> 37:27.576
THIS SITE'S TAKEN ON
A LIFE OF ITS OWN.

37:27.576 --> 37:29.418
EVERYBODY'S GOT A STORY.

37:29.418 --> 37:31.680
JUST TRYING TO CORROBORATE
WHAT THEY SAW.

37:31.680 --> 37:34.683
YOU KNOW, IT'S SO FUNNY.

37:34.683 --> 37:38.527
I'VE NEVER HAD
THAT "TICKING CLOCK" FEELING.

37:38.527 --> 37:41.760
YOU KNOW, I'VE NEVER EVEN
HAD THE URGE TO HAVE A BABY.

37:41.760 --> 37:44.793
THERE I WAS...

37:44.793 --> 37:46.495
(whoosh)

37:46.495 --> 37:47.936
(speaks inaudibly)

37:47.936 --> 37:49.738
SOME BLONDE WOMAN

37:49.738 --> 37:51.940
GIVING ME AN ULTRASOUND.

37:51.940 --> 37:53.702
(Demetri) THIS SONOGRAPHER...

37:53.702 --> 37:56.044
MAYBE SHE SAW YOU, TOO.

37:56.044 --> 37:58.847
MAYBE SHE'S OUT THERE
SOMEWHERE,

37:58.847 --> 38:01.910
WAITIN' FOR YOU
TO POST SOMETHING.

38:01.910 --> 38:04.353
YEAH.

38:04.353 --> 38:05.614
(smacks lips) WHY NOT?

38:06.885 --> 38:09.858
(exhales deeply)

38:13.762 --> 38:15.494
(whoosh)
I WANNA KNOW.

38:15.494 --> 38:17.866
IT'S A GIRL.

38:17.866 --> 38:20.969
(crying)

38:20.969 --> 38:24.573
(sniffles) OKAY.

38:24.573 --> 38:27.406
(typing)

38:27.406 --> 38:28.877
THERE.

38:28.877 --> 38:31.309
YOUR TURN.

38:31.309 --> 38:34.012
I DIDN'T SEE ANYTHING,
JANIS.

38:34.012 --> 38:35.684
YEAH, YOU KNOW,

38:35.684 --> 38:38.387
SOME PEOPLE JUST THINK
THAT MEANS YOU'LL BE ASLEEP.

38:38.387 --> 38:40.849
OR IT MEANS I'LL BE DEAD.

38:40.849 --> 38:42.351
(scoffs)

38:44.853 --> 38:48.527
I MET A WOMAN TODAY
WHO DIDN'T HAVE A VISION.

38:50.559 --> 38:53.862
FIVE MINUTES AFTER SHE TOLD ME,
SHE WAS SHOT AND KILLED.

38:55.864 --> 39:00.038
HAVE YOU TALKED TO ZOEY
ABOUT THIS?

39:00.038 --> 39:02.441
IN MY EXPERIENCE, UM,

39:02.441 --> 39:03.942
FIANCÃ©ES AREN'T REALLY BIG

39:03.942 --> 39:06.515
ON THEIR GROOMS DYING
BEFORE THE WEDDING.

39:06.515 --> 39:08.517
RUINS THE FIRST DANCE.
YEAH.

39:08.517 --> 39:10.048
HEAVY CORPSE.
(chuckles)

39:10.048 --> 39:12.421
IT'S BAD WEDDING ETIQUETTE
OR SOMETHING.

39:12.421 --> 39:15.654
(laughs)

39:15.654 --> 39:18.557
OKAY, IF YOU'RE GONNA
BE DEAD--

39:18.557 --> 39:20.559
AND THAT'S A BIG "IF"...

39:23.031 --> 39:25.764
DON'T YOU KINDA WANNA KNOW
HOW IT HAPPENS?

39:28.467 --> 39:30.098
I DON'T KNOW.

39:32.641 --> 39:35.143
I DON'T THINK SO.

39:36.745 --> 39:39.748
YEAH, BUT IF YOU KNOW,
MAYBE YOU CAN PREVENT IT.

39:42.050 --> 39:44.052
AND MAYBE THERE'S SOMEBODY
OUT THERE

39:44.052 --> 39:46.915
THAT HAS INFORMATION
THAT CAN HELP YOU.

39:49.818 --> 39:51.990
WHAT THE HELL.

39:57.626 --> 40:00.028
(sighs)

40:00.028 --> 40:03.031
(typing)

40:10.008 --> 40:12.541
(fire crackling)

40:12.541 --> 40:15.614
HEY,
IT'S 3:00 IN THE MORNING.

40:15.614 --> 40:19.748
DIDN'T WANT TO WAKE YOU.
GOT BACK LATE.

40:19.748 --> 40:21.019
GINGER ALE?

40:21.019 --> 40:22.190
NO.

40:28.997 --> 40:31.159
HOW WAS NEVADA?

40:32.901 --> 40:35.534
UTAH.

40:35.534 --> 40:37.005
DEAD END.

40:38.767 --> 40:40.068
YOU ALL RIGHT?

40:43.742 --> 40:45.744
AT WORK, I'M MAKING MOVES,

40:45.744 --> 40:48.747
BETTING THE FUTURE
IS GONNA HAPPEN AS I SAW IT.

40:48.747 --> 40:51.079
BUT HERE AT HOME,
WITH YOU...

40:51.079 --> 40:53.952
I'M PRAYING IT DOESN'T.

40:56.224 --> 40:57.886
(sets down glass)

40:59.958 --> 41:05.664
DID I DO THE RIGHT THING,
TELLING YOU ABOUT LLOYD?

41:05.664 --> 41:06.965
YOU DID.

41:10.038 --> 41:12.040
WE SHOULDN'T KEEP SECRETS
FROM EACH OTHER.

41:12.040 --> 41:14.242
(whoosh)

41:20.749 --> 41:23.011
WHY'D YOU MAKE A FIRE?

41:23.011 --> 41:25.013
(whispers) NO REASON.

41:35.023 --> 41:38.496
(cell phone rings)

41:38.496 --> 41:39.828
THIS IS DEMETRI.

41:39.828 --> 41:42.130
(woman) Mr. Noh,
I'm sorry to disturb you,

41:42.130 --> 41:45.804
but I'm calling in response
to your Mosaic board posting.

41:45.804 --> 41:49.177
MY POST? ALREADY? WHO IS THIS?
HOW'D YOU GET THIS NUMBER?

41:49.177 --> 41:52.981
I CAN'T DIVULGE THAT, BUT I CAN
TELL YOU MY VISION INVOLVED YOU.

41:52.981 --> 41:56.014
GO ON.

41:56.014 --> 41:58.887
IN MY FLASH-FORWARD,

41:58.887 --> 42:01.289
I WAS READING
AN INTELLIGENCE BRIEFING,

42:01.289 --> 42:04.022
AND... I AM SORRY.

42:04.022 --> 42:06.524
THERE IS
NO DELICATE WAY TO SAY THIS,

42:06.524 --> 42:11.259
BUT ON MARCH 15th, 2010,

42:11.259 --> 42:13.662
YOU ARE GOING TO BE MURDERED.

42:45.634 --> 42:46.965
YOU'RE HOME, DADDY.

42:46.965 --> 42:49.938
(whispers) SORRY, SWEETIE.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO WAKE YOU.

42:49.938 --> 42:51.940
GO BACK TO SLEEP.

42:53.942 --> 42:55.944
DADDY?

42:55.944 --> 42:57.245
(normal voice) YEAH?

42:57.245 --> 43:01.149
THE REASON
I WAS BAD AT SCHOOL--

43:01.149 --> 43:03.852
IT'S 'CAUSE THE OTHER KIDS
WERE SAYING

43:03.852 --> 43:06.785
THE FLASH-FORWARDS
ARE GONNA COME TRUE.

43:06.785 --> 43:09.918
ONLY THE GOOD ONES, HONEY.
I PROMISE.

43:09.918 --> 43:13.191
SO IF THE BAD ONES
AREN'T GONNA COME TRUE,

43:13.191 --> 43:15.193
WHY DID PEOPLE HAVE THEM?

43:17.025 --> 43:19.027
THINK OF 'EM LIKE A WARNING.

43:19.027 --> 43:21.169
YOU KNOW,
LIKE WHEN MOMMY'S DRIVING

43:21.169 --> 43:24.232
